pageContext.claim: “They have been taken so far left, where Pocahontas is now considered a conservative in the Democrat Party. She's like a conservative person, Pocahontas Elizabeth Warren, she's considered like a conservative person.”
pageContext.analysis: This is a stretch. The party has moved to the left, in part because of the popularity of Sen. Bernie Sanders (I-Vt.) but Warren remains one of the most liberal members of the party.
